Class ChildDetailInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.emmes.aps.medication.ChildDetailInfo

  • public class ChildDetailInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    The Class ChildDetailInfo is for handling the list item detail info. The medication is dislayed in a list by the listactivity MedicationListActivity. The list item is the object of type ChildDetailsInfo.
